        "Name" : "Letter Of Marque Marik",
        "Details" : "Darius comes smiling. \"We have received a interesting proposal from [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreAndurien],Andurien]]. It appears that Duchess Catherine Humphreys may be interested in issuing us a letter of marque so that we can perform supplemental contracts for the Free Worlds League.\" \r\n\r\n\"Which, as well all know means that we'll likely be working for the Duchy of Andurien rather than [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreJanosMarik],Janos Marik]]\". Yang adds.\r\n\r\nDarius continues. \"Yeah, no hiding that fact. But they'll provide JumpShip access to Marik space and any flashpoints that the League might be interested in. It's just a way for them to go around the official way for contracts.\"\r\n\r\n\"I know for a fact that I could use a return to more civilized space. What's the catch here?\" Sumire's face brightens at the idea.\r\n\r\n\"None, except that if we sign up with Marik, we can't expect other such offers from the other major factions in the area until we complete their missions. Otherwise, it's a clear deal Commander.\" Darius continues.\r\n\r\n\"We can also contact either Steiner or Kurita's representatives and present them with this offer to see if they have an interest in our services. But we won't get the travel access to Marik space\".",
